00:40:27,543 --> 00:40:28,594
Coach, I'm sorry.

1006
00:40:28,678 --> 00:40:30,145
I was just looking out
for the team.

1007
00:40:30,212 --> 00:40:33,749
Did you mean what you wrote?

1008
00:40:33,816 --> 00:40:36,218
That you're worried I'm not
as focused on the Cheerios!

1009
00:40:36,286 --> 00:40:37,886
as I used to be?

1010
00:40:37,937 --> 00:40:39,438
Well, then you don't
need be sorry.

1011
00:40:39,522 --> 00:40:41,773
And thank you for the feedback.

1012
00:40:41,858 --> 00:40:43,224
You're not mad?

1013
00:40:43,276 --> 00:40:44,693
No, Becky.

1014
00:40:44,744 --> 00:40:46,111
(sighs)

1015
00:40:46,195 --> 00:40:49,915
But impending motherhood
doth given me perspective.

1016
00:40:49,999 --> 00:40:53,735
Oh, Becky, I'm reminded
of all my passions: winning,

1017
00:40:53,786 --> 00:40:55,003
my girls,

1018
00:40:55,071 --> 00:40:56,872
destroying my enemies.

1019
00:40:56,923 --> 00:40:58,540
Motherhood's not gonna
change that.

1020
00:40:58,591 --> 00:41:01,343
If anything, it makes me
want them far more.

1021
00:41:01,410 --> 00:41:03,962
You're an excellent
co-captain, Becky.

1022
00:41:04,047 --> 00:41:05,847
You're like me.

1023
00:41:05,915 --> 00:41:07,582
Not afraid to make
the tough calls.

1024
00:41:07,634 --> 00:41:08,900
Coach?

1025
00:41:08,968 --> 00:41:10,218
You're gonna be a great mom.

1026
00:41:22,264 --> 00:41:24,950
(school bell ringing)

1027
00:41:37,947 --> 00:41:39,948
There you are, baby.
You ready?

1028
00:41:39,999 --> 00:41:41,967
For lunch.

1029
00:41:42,051 --> 00:41:43,301
We're going
off-campus, right?

1030
00:41:43,386 --> 00:41:44,836
Hey, Sam.

1031
00:41:57,567 --> 00:41:59,901
(school bell ringing faintly)

1032
00:42:05,191 --> 00:42:06,525
What's all this?

1033
00:42:11,781 --> 00:42:15,617
"So You Were A Jerk
To Your Fiance."

1034
00:42:17,286 --> 00:42:20,672
Not particularly clever,
but I appreciate your pith.

1035
00:42:22,208 --> 00:42:25,794
(laughs):
"Congratulations--
I Love You."

1036
00:42:25,845 --> 00:42:27,262
These are wonderful.

1037
00:42:27,329 --> 00:42:28,663
They're wonderful.

1038
00:42:28,715 --> 00:42:30,098
(both chuckle)

1039
00:42:30,166 --> 00:42:33,168
A little myopic maybe,
but a great first effort.

1040
00:42:37,056 --> 00:42:38,607
I'm so proud of you.

1041
00:42:38,674 --> 00:42:41,560
So do I call you Professor
or Madam or what?

1042
00:42:41,644 --> 00:42:43,311
I'm not sure of
the protocol here.

1043
00:42:43,362 --> 00:42:44,563
No, no, no,
it's just tenure.

1044
00:42:44,647 --> 00:42:45,847
You can call me Emma.

1045
00:42:45,898 --> 00:42:48,349
Or sweetheart
or cutie pie or doll-face.

1046
00:42:48,401 --> 00:42:49,451
Or Professor Doll-Face.
Ooh.

1047
00:42:49,518 --> 00:42:50,535
I like Professor Doll-Face.

1048
00:42:50,620 --> 00:42:52,704
(laughs)

1049
00:42:52,789 --> 00:42:54,122
(clears throat)

1050
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:56,191
My first marriage didn't
work out because my wife

1051
00:42:56,242 --> 00:42:57,459
didn't believe in me.

1052
00:42:57,526 --> 00:43:01,413
And then I go and pull
the same crap on you.

1053
00:43:01,497 --> 00:43:05,333
All I know is that right now,
in this moment,

1054
00:43:05,384 --> 00:43:08,920
I just want it to stop.

1055
00:43:09,005 --> 00:43:13,225
I want to sit here, eat
some chicken and look back on

1056
00:43:13,309 --> 00:43:15,343
everything you've done
to get to this moment

1057
00:43:15,394 --> 00:43:19,314
and everything I'm going to do
from this moment on

1058
00:43:19,381 --> 00:43:23,885
to make sure you feel...
as special... and amazing

1059
00:43:23,936 --> 00:43:26,655
as I know you are.

